      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "🛠 STACK (alles Custom-Python)\n\n• openai SDK 1.40+   → OpenAI-API-kompatibler DGX-Client\n• pydantic-settings  → typed Config aus env + Streamlit-secrets\n• supabase-py        → DB via PostgREST (kein direkter PG-Connect)\n• httpx              → Tavily Web-Search-Calls\n• ThreadPoolExecutor → parallele Sub-Lookups\n• streamlit 1.37     → UI + Multi-Turn-Session-State\n\nNICHT verwendet (bewusst):\n  ✗ LangChain  (zu schwergewichtig)\n  ✗ LlamaIndex (RAG-only, zu komplex)\n  ✗ CrewAI/AutoGen (Multi-Agent Overkill)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🛠 STACK (alles Custom-Python)\n\n• openai SDK 1.40+   → OpenAI-API-kompatibler DGX-Client\n• pydantic-settings  → typed Config aus env + Streamlit-secrets\n• supabase-py        → DB via PostgREST (kein direkter PG-Connect)\n• httpx              → Tavily Web-Search-Calls\n• ThreadPoolExecutor → parallele Sub-Lookups\n• streamlit 1.37     → UI + Multi-Turn-Session-State\n\nNICHT verwendet (bewusst):\n  ✗ LangChain  (zu schwergewichtig)\n  ✗ LlamaIndex (RAG-only, zu komplex)\n  ✗ CrewAI/AutoGen (Multi-Agent Overkill)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
