      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "🧠 LLM-LAYER  (falken_kb/genai/dgx_client.py)\n\nDGXClient ─ Thin Wrapper um openai.OpenAI\n├─ Endpoint: pgxapi.siller.io/v1 (DGX, self-hosted)\n├─ Modelle: gemma (Chat) + nomic-embed-text (768d)\n└─ Modell-Fallback-Chain bei Rate-Limit\n\nCustom-Methoden:\n  chat(messages, ...) → plain text\n  chat_with_schema(messages, json_schema, required_keys)\n    ├─ probiert all_models bis valides JSON kommt\n    ├─ _parse_json_loose: 3-Stufen-Recovery\n    │   (direkt → markdown-strip → {...}-Extract)\n    └─ defensive .get() in allen Handlern\n\n  embed(texts) → list[768d-float]",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🧠 LLM-LAYER  (falken_kb/genai/dgx_client.py)\n\nDGXClient ─ Thin Wrapper um openai.OpenAI\n├─ Endpoint: pgxapi.siller.io/v1 (DGX, self-hosted)\n├─ Modelle: gemma (Chat) + nomic-embed-text (768d)\n└─ Modell-Fallback-Chain bei Rate-Limit\n\nCustom-Methoden:\n  chat(messages, ...) → plain text\n  chat_with_schema(messages, json_schema, required_keys)\n    ├─ probiert all_models bis valides JSON kommt\n    ├─ _parse_json_loose: 3-Stufen-Recovery\n    │   (direkt → markdown-strip → {...}-Extract)\n    └─ defensive .get() in allen Handlern\n\n  embed(texts) → list[768d-float]",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
