      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "🔧 SQL-SANITIZER  (db.sanitize_llm_sql)\n\nPost-processing der LLM-generierten SQL:\n\n  • ODER BY → ORDER BY (German keyword fix)\n  • YEAR(CURDATE()) → EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE)\n  • JOIN x JOIN x ON → JOIN x ON (token-doubling)\n  • player_name → player (typo-correction)\n  • falken_skater_skater_stats → falken_skater_stats\n  • '2008/ '2008/09' → '2008/09' (broken strings)\n\n+ Retry-on-Syntax-Error in fact_sql.py:\n  - 1. try mit temp=0.05 (deterministic)\n  - 2. try mit temp=0.2 + Hinweis was schief lief",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🔧 SQL-SANITIZER  (db.sanitize_llm_sql)\n\nPost-processing der LLM-generierten SQL:\n\n  • ODER BY → ORDER BY (German keyword fix)\n  • YEAR(CURDATE()) → EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE)\n  • JOIN x JOIN x ON → JOIN x ON (token-doubling)\n  • player_name → player (typo-correction)\n  • falken_skater_skater_stats → falken_skater_stats\n  • '2008/ '2008/09' → '2008/09' (broken strings)\n\n+ Retry-on-Syntax-Error in fact_sql.py:\n  - 1. try mit temp=0.05 (deterministic)\n  - 2. try mit temp=0.2 + Hinweis was schief lief",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
