      "text": "MODE 1: Direct-DB\n\nPattern: Single-Shot\n\nTrigger: _is_simple_db_\nquestion() = True\n(Heuristik: Jahr+Stat-Wort)\n\nFlow:\n1. fact_sql(q)\n   ├─ LLM: NL→SQL\n   ├─ Sanitize\n   ├─ Postgres\n   └─ LLM: Synth\n\n~30s · 3 LLM-Calls",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MODE 1: Direct-DB\n\nPattern: Single-Shot\n\nTrigger: _is_simple_db_\nquestion() = True\n(Heuristik: Jahr+Stat-Wort)\n\nFlow:\n1. fact_sql(q)\n   ├─ LLM: NL→SQL\n   ├─ Sanitize\n   ├─ Postgres\n   └─ LLM: Synth\n\n~30s · 3 LLM-Calls",
      "autoResize": true,
