      "text": "MODE 2: RAG\n\nPattern: Embed-Search-Synth\n\nTrigger: classify=narrative\n(LLM-Router)\n\nFlow:\n1. embed(q) → 768d\n2. pgvector top-K=6\n3. LLM: Synth mit\n   Quellen-Zitaten\n\n~30s · 1 LLM-Call\n+ 1 embed-Call",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MODE 2: RAG\n\nPattern: Embed-Search-Synth\n\nTrigger: classify=narrative\n(LLM-Router)\n\nFlow:\n1. embed(q) → 768d\n2. pgvector top-K=6\n3. LLM: Synth mit\n   Quellen-Zitaten\n\n~30s · 1 LLM-Call\n+ 1 embed-Call",
