      "text": "MODE 3: Multi-Hop\n\nPattern: Plan-and-Execute\n(hybrid_web.py)\n\nTrigger: Keyword-Hint\n(besitzer/restaurant/...)\n\nFlow:\n1. Tavily Web-Search\n2. LLM: Extract persons\n3. ThreadPool: parallel\n   lookup_player(name)\n4. LLM: Synth\n\n~60s · 2 LLM + N parallel",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MODE 3: Multi-Hop\n\nPattern: Plan-and-Execute\n(hybrid_web.py)\n\nTrigger: Keyword-Hint\n(besitzer/restaurant/...)\n\nFlow:\n1. Tavily Web-Search\n2. LLM: Extract persons\n3. ThreadPool: parallel\n   lookup_player(name)\n4. LLM: Synth\n\n~60s · 2 LLM + N parallel",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
