      "text": "MODE 4: Tool-Agent\n\nPattern: ReAct-Loop\n(tool_agent.py, experimental)\n\nTrigger: USE_TOOL_AGENT=true\n(default OFF, instabil mit\nDGX-Gemma ohne native\ntool-use-API)\n\nFlow: max 3 Iterations,\nLLM wählt Tool, sieht\nResult, entscheidet next\n\n~80-120s · N+1 LLM-Calls",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MODE 4: Tool-Agent\n\nPattern: ReAct-Loop\n(tool_agent.py, experimental)\n\nTrigger: USE_TOOL_AGENT=true\n(default OFF, instabil mit\nDGX-Gemma ohne native\ntool-use-API)\n\nFlow: max 3 Iterations,\nLLM wählt Tool, sieht\nResult, entscheidet next\n\n~80-120s · N+1 LLM-Calls",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
